    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone looking for a functional daily driver. The engine runs consistently and the car handles well on the road, though it is due for some routine maintenance and shows visible signs of wear and tear, including minor exterior scratches and a well-used interior. It is a solid choice for a buyer who prioritizes utility over aesthetics and is prepared for some upcoming service requirements.",
