      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available now is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. This example has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a full double-VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement to ensure mechanical longevity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission delivers tactile shifts, paired with a factory-spec variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. The chassis remains structurally flawless with no signs of subframe fatigue. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior retains its factory-fresh matte finish. This is a meticulously preserved specimen for the enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
